社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"451227bf6d347caf066a3b21efa9ff0f158e1308","tid":2068342,"uid":46702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"有奶便是娘 明天又爆升了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e651721935abd5ae9d3985e25dbe0cf303a8b2a2","tid":2068342,"uid":211062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"Drop"},{"pid":"2cf344489a6032dadafdba8d2cabb14492e9360b","tid":2068342,"uid":339550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:29:47.000Z","msg":"熱刺贊助商"},{"pid":"0b0dbe6a3ddcb80d40c77bd4d1543c444a41d355","tid":2068342,"uid":46702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e651721935abd5ae9d3985e25dbe0cf303a8b2a2","tid":2068342,"uid":211062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"Drop"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:43:17.000Z","msg":"只會升 國家隊進場"}]}